{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1910, "height": 2627, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "出资护树碑", "block_bbox": [254, 234, 464, 274], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "闻之古云：日星为天文，草木为地文。因知市镇村落间乔木古树大石森口，非独观瞻所系，实为风气所关也。盖其始也，由人力之栽培，及其盘根固英□茂口者，以为此天造地设不可复口云。兹村有古槐一株，大十抱，高数十□，历年久□，不可复记□有欲卖此树者，将召木工伐之。窃思召伯遗爱甘棠志石迹表乔松口树枝口古天口积千年，实闻此村之□气口口是合村人等共议口口口木造作，官不得私卖私□□□不朽，且令后之人□□□暗明□□□□之光矣。是为序。\n", "block_bbox": [163, 293, 1134, 875], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "府庠生杜含章拜撰", "block_bbox": [249, 894, 581, 933], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜兴邦敬书", "block_bbox": [369, 955, 579, 995], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "出口资人等姓氏开列于后：", "block_bbox": [250, 1016, 717, 1058], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "计开", "block_bbox": [249, 1076, 341, 1115], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1159, 240, 1576, 989], "block_id": 6, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜允举 李口德杜口茵杜口□杜口友 杜□□杜口□杜口口杜成秀□□□□□杜□□杜廷用杜廷□杜廷行□□□口有德杜希天杜天德杜文天李天章李天秀杜口□杜口成杜口□\n", "block_bbox": [248, 1140, 1459, 1363], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "时乾隆伍拾口年陆月吉日", "block_bbox": [251, 1382, 701, 1424], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "注：此碑无碑题，碑文收入宗谱时撰碑名。", "block_bbox": [253, 1447, 999, 1488], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "杜公独建舞楼碑记", "block_bbox": [253, 1570, 589, 1608], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公讳允峰，字早庵，坻坞口口人也。幼颖慧，长博洽，后游太学，尝周急恤乏，有古侠烈风。至其器宇宏深，识量豁达，尤为县公、庶尹、缙绅、先生所推重。故闻公之名，无论识与不识，莫不时切景仰云。公诵《帝君阴骘文》，有创修寺院、印造经文等语，公尤留意焉。故兹村有关帝庙，年久圮毁，公欲择地创修，幸众有同志，公仅捐资五千，而已告峻。尚有舞楼未建，众方默然，而公慨然以身任之。以为庙宇巍焕，有妥神之所，而可无侑神之资于？考之诗云：籥舞笙歌，乐具和奏。又曰：神之听之，既和且平。且礼重宫悬，豫繁殷荐。而书称：典乐亦命伯夔，则侑神亦钜典也。况表孙叔之绩，犹假优孟衣", "block_bbox": [169, 1631, 1105, 2354], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1138, 1505, 1580, 2392], "block_id": 12, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1692, 703, 1766, 1373], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三八〇", "block_bbox": [1697, 1993, 1748, 2106], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 13}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.984791100025177, "coordinate": [169.67120361328125, 1631.520751953125, 1105.192626953125, 2354.181884765625]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9816908240318298, "coordinate": [1159.382568359375, 240.331298828125, 1576.430419921875, 989.4453125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9812147617340088, "coordinate": [163.66659545898438, 293.9366455078125, 1134.5054931640625, 875.3729248046875]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9807878732681274, "coordinate": [1138.83251953125, 1505.319580078125, 1580.900146484375, 2392.826904296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.949097752571106, "coordinate": [248.50897216796875, 1140.9119873046875, 1459.28271484375, 1363.3631591796875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8838794231414795, "coordinate": [253.1668701171875, 1447.1312255859375, 999.87353515625, 1488.8704833984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8589688539505005, "coordinate": [250.8474884033203, 1016.564208984375, 717.7494506835938, 1058.851074